data.description: LOCATION! LOCATION! LOCATION!  This charming Tudor-Style Cottage, all brick home is located downtown Charleston near the Citadel, Hampton Park and Ashley River!  This home has a lot of history!  Wagener Terrace is a desirable area and here is your chance to turn this home into whatever you want and make it spectacular!  NO HOA!  The home currently has 4 bedrooms and two bathrooms.  Two bedrooms and one bath is located on the mail level while the other two bedrooms and bath is upstairs. New roof was put on March 2023.  HOME IS BEING SOLD  AS-IS, SELLER TO MAKE NO REPAIRS.  This home needs some tender loving care.
